I have successfully added sound notifications to the Pomodoro timer. When a work or break interval ends, a sound will now play to alert the user.

This completes the goal I set out to achieve. The project is now a more user-friendly and effective productivity tool.

The following changes were made:
*   A `requirements.txt` file was created to manage the `beepy` dependency.
*   The `pomodoro.py` script was updated to import the `beepy` library and trigger a sound at the end of each countdown.
